    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/2",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">Also, reestimate parameters using best-practice statistical procedures. Experience shows that simple, but robust models tend to work better than more ambitious, but fragile models. It is essential to monitor and control model performance over time.</p>",
